title: Walk On Water

Light de light, we got mornin',

Mornin' makes another day

Glory sight, got de dawnin'

Lordy, light the night away



Light de light, we got de mornin',

Mornin' makes another day

Glory sight, got de dawnin'

Lordy, light the night away



Light de light, we got mornin',

Mornin' makes another day

She walks on water,

Ah, ain't it like her
